== Hello! ヤッホー ==
You found me! I'm [https://vrchat.com/home/user/usr_8ee44c1a-f905-4e08-bb61-e1cd34e09fc0 DAG] (he/they), a [[VRChat Wiki]] [[VRCWiki:Team|Maintainer]], and long-time user since 2018. VRChat has changed my life. I hope you find something eye-opening on this Wiki. Thanks for checking out my page! Add to my [[User_talk:Usr_8ee44c1a-f905-4e08-bb61-e1cd34e09fc0|Talk page]] if you need to discuss something. Join the VRChat Wiki [[Discord servers|Discord server]] if you wish to talk more.

Even before working on the VRChat Wiki, I wrote wiki-styled articles about VRChat and adjacent topics on a website called [https://en.wikifur.com/wiki/WikiFur_Furry_Central Wikifur]. When I was in college for a short while in 2022, I submit a scholarly essay called "[https://docs.google.com/document/d/1OMnK2jWZZVGa0JKDj-qdr8dOR6jKoUKP/edit?usp=sharing&ouid=117718509159178239703 The Importance of Avatars in a Virtual World]", which was graded an 96%. Meta once let me publish an [https://www.meta.com/blog/quest/demeo-fathers-day-dungeons-dragons-beat-saber-ragnarock article] about me and my father, for Father's Day 2023.

